---
// About Section — The Compliance Binder Differentiator
---

<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Left: visual -->
      <div class="about-visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="binder-card">
          <div class="binder-tab">COMPLIANCE BINDER</div>
          <ul class="binder-toc">
            <li><span class="toc-num">01</span><span class="toc-item">Infrastructure Configuration Register</span></li>
            <li><span class="toc-num">02</span><span class="toc-item">Identity & Access Policy</span></li>
            <li><span class="toc-num">03</span><span class="toc-item">DR Test Results & RTO Log</span></li>
            <li><span class="toc-num">04</span><span class="toc-item">Regulatory Gap Analysis Report</span></li>
            <li><span class="toc-num">05</span><span class="toc-item">Change Management Records</span></li>
            <li><span class="toc-num">06</span><span class="toc-item">Audit Trail & Evidence Package</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="binder-badge">
            <span class="badge-icon">✔</span>
            Living Document — Always Current
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-deco-text" aria-hidden="true">IF IT ISN'T DOCUMENTED,<br />IT DIDN'T HAPPEN.</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: content -->
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="accent-line"></div>
        <p class="section-label">Our Differentiator</p>
        <h2 class="section-heading">
          The <span class="accent-text">Compliance Binder</span><br />
          Changes Everything.
        </h2>
        <p class="about-body">
          Rooted in FDA/cGMP validation methodology, we operate by a principle that separates serious
          infrastructure partners from commodity vendors: <strong class="highlight">if it isn't documented,
          it didn't happen.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="about-body">
          Every engagement we deliver includes a <strong class="highlight">Compliance Binder</strong> —
          a living, structured repository of configurations, policies, test results, and audit evidence.
          When regulators arrive, you hand them the binder. When something changes, the binder changes.
          When auditors ask questions, the answers are already written down.
        </p>
        <p class="about-body">
          For a busy business owner or compliance officer, that binder is worth its weight in gold.
        </p>

        <div class="expertise-chips">
          <span class="chip">FDA / cGMP</span>
          <span class="chip">NIST CSF</span>
          <span class="chip">FINRA</span>
          <span class="chip">ISO 27001</span>
          <span class="chip">Microsoft Intune</span>
          <span class="chip">Authentik IdP</span>
          <span class="chip">YubiKey / MFA</span>
          <span class="chip">Disaster Recovery</span>
        </div>

        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          Start Your Readiness Assessment
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .accent-text { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .highlight { color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600; }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Visual side */
  .about-visual {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .binder-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card), var(--shadow-accent);
  }

  .binder-tab {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #0f1624;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.6rem var(--space-xl);
  }

  .binder-toc {
    list-style: none;
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .binder-toc li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .binder-toc li:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }

  .toc-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .binder-badge {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: 0.75rem var(--space-xl);
    background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.07);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.2);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: #4ade80;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .badge-icon { font-size: 0.7rem; }

  .about-deco-text {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(212, 160, 23, 0.18);
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* Content side */
  .about-content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 58ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .expertise-chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .chip {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: var(--color-accent-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-visual { order: 2; }
    .about-content { order: 1; }
  }
</style>
